### Metrics Ingestion API

# Ingest a single metric payload
POST https://metrics-api.nexus.io/api/v2/metrics/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "hostname": "db-primary-01",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:30:00Z",
  "metrics": {
    "latency_ms": 312,
    "iops": 24000,
    "cpu_percent": 71,
    "memory_percent": 82
  }
}

### Query P99 latency for a host
GET https://metrics-api.nexus.io/api/v2/metrics/query
    ?host=db-primary-01
    &window=2h
    &percentile=99
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### List all monitored hosts
GET https://metrics-api.nexus.io/api/v2/hosts
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get host health status
GET https://metrics-api.nexus.io/api/v2/hosts/db-primary-01/health
Authorization: Bearer <token>
